data.description: Charming 4 Bedroom/2 Bathroom home in Mebane in Collington Farms. Features nice open living room. Kitchen with lots of counter space and stainless steel appliances. 3 bedrooms all on main level. Master bedroom with full bath attached, walk-in closet. Upstairs bonus room. Fenced backyard. Incredible community just minutes from downtown Mebane. Don't miss your chance to see this one! Also sellers loan is assumable.
